						<div class="postbody">In other words:
<br />
<br />For 8-bit output:
<br /><div class="codetitle"><b>Code:</b></div><div class="codecontent">sample = value ^ 0x80;</div><br /><br />For 16-bit output:<br /><div class="codetitle"><b>Code:</b></div><div class="codecontent">sample = value ^ 0x8000;</div></div>

					
